# Root Environment Variables
# This file is for reference only - actual .env files should be in apps/server and apps/client

# ====================================
# Quick Start
# ====================================
# 1. Copy apps/server/.env.example to apps/server/.env
# 2. Copy apps/client/.env.example to apps/client/.env (optional)
# 3. Update the values in both files
# 4. Run: bun install
# 5. Run: bun run dev

# See individual .env.example files in each app directory for detailed configuration:
# - apps/server/.env.example - Backend configuration
# - apps/client/.env.example - Frontend configuration (optional)